definitions.definition: ( UK dialectal , Northern England , Scotland ) Cream ; also, the creamlike froth on ale or other liquor; froth or foam in general.

main_definition: ( UK dialectal , Northern England , Scotland ) Cream ; also, the creamlike froth on ale or other liquor; froth or foam in general.

definitions.definition: A bundle , package , or quantity of paper , nowadays usually containing 500 sheets .
An abstract large amount of something.
examples: I can't go – I still have reams of work left.

main_definition: A bundle , package , or quantity of paper , nowadays usually containing 500 sheets .
secondary_definitions: ( chiefly in the plural ) An abstract large amount of something.
